A lecturer at the Department of Technical Education, Hassan Usman Polytechnic Katsina, Dr. Bello Birchi, has been kidnapped. Birchi was whisked away at his country home, at about midnight yesterday at Tashar Bara’u village along Dutsinma road in Katsina state.
ALSO READ:Kastina notorious kidnapper nabbed
 The chairman of Academic Staff Union of the Polytechnic (ASUP), Dr Sabi’u Yau Abdullahi, who confirmed the development said the union is greatly disturbed over the unfortunate incidence.

 “No communication so far has been made with the abductors.” he added.

